    {
        "source_sentence": "不行眼識過去未來現在本性清淨不清淨、開顯不開顯、寂靜不寂靜、遠離不遠離，不行耳、鼻、舌、身、意識過去未來現在本性清淨不清淨、開顯不開顯、寂靜不寂靜、遠離不遠離。",
        "from": "T07n0220o_600:1106a26_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善勇猛！",
        "from": "T07n0220o_600:1106a26_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若諸菩薩能如是行，速能圓滿一切智法。",
        "from": "T07n0220o_600:1106a27_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「復次，善勇猛！",
        "from": "T07n0220o_600:1106a28_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若諸菩薩修行般若波羅蜜多，不恃執色，不恃執受、想、行、識；",
        "from": "T07n0220o_600:1106a29_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不恃執眼，不恃執耳、鼻、舌、身、意；",
        "from": "T07n0220o_600:1106b01_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不恃執色，不恃執聲、香、味、觸、法；",
        "from": "T07n0220o_600:1106b02_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不恃執眼識，不恃執耳、鼻、舌、身、意識；",
        "from": "T07n0220o_600:1106b02_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不恃執色清淨，不恃執受、想、行、識清淨；",
        "from": "T07n0220o_600:1106b03_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不恃執眼清淨，不恃執耳、鼻、舌、身、意清淨；",
        "from": "T07n0220o_600:1106b04_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不恃執色清淨，不恃執聲、香、味、觸、法清淨；",
        "from": "T07n0220o_600:1106b05_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不恃執眼識清淨，不恃執耳、鼻、舌、身、意識清淨；",
        "from": "T07n0220o_600:1106b06_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "不恃執色所緣清淨，不恃執受、想、行、識所緣清淨；",
